>>> def compute(a, b, c):
...     return (a + b) * c
...
>>> compute(4, 1, 3)
15
>>> compute([1],[2,3],2)
[1, 2, 3, 1, 2, 3]
>>> compute('l','olo',4)
'lolololololololo'



print('"Yes," he said.')    # => "Yes," he said. 
print("\"Yes,\" he said.")  # => "Yes," he said. 
print('"Isn\'t," she said.')  # => "Isn't," she said

关于string的用法：
‘’和“”是一样的，可以混用
str（string）
'world' in 'hello world'
len(String)
str.find(substr)
